yaar Tune Kya Kiya (TV series)|Pyaar Tune Kya Kiya]]'' || Pari || [[Zing TV]]\n|-\n| 2014&ndash;2015 || ''[[Box Cricket League|Box Cricket League 1]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.india.com/showbiz/box-cricket-league-teams-bcl-2014-team-details-with-tv-actors-names-of-celebrities-221217/|title=Box Cricket League Teams: BCL 2014 Team Details With TV Actors & Names of Celebrities|work=india.com|accessdate=14 December 2014|date=14 December 2014}}</ref> || Contestant || [[Sony Entertainment Television]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2015 || ''[[Code Red (Indian TV series)|Code Red\u2014Talaash]]''|| Host || rowspan=\"2\"|[[Colors TV]]\n|-\n| ''[[Jhalak Dikhhla Jaa (season 8)|Jhalak Dikhhla Jaa 8]]'' || Contestant\n|-\n| ''[[Comedy Classes]]'' || [[Life OK]]\n|-\n| 2015&ndash;2017 || ''[[Comedy Nights Bachao]]''|| rowspan=2|[[Colors TV]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\"| 2016 || ''[[Krishnadasi (2016 TV series)|Krishnadasi]]'' || Guest\n|-\n| ''[[Bahu Hamari Rajni Kant]]'' || Priya || [[Life OK]]\n|-\n| ''[[Box Cricket League|Box Cricket League 2]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/200-Actors-10-Teams-and-1-Winner-Let-The-Game-Begin/articleshow/50219718.cms|title=200 Actors, 10 Teams, and 1 Winner... Let The Game Begin|work=The Times of India|accessdate=4 March 2016}}</ref> || Contestant || rowspan=3|[[Colors TV]]\n|-\n| ''[[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 9)|Bigg Boss 9]]'' || rowspan=2|Guest\n|-\n| ''[[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 10)|Bigg Boss 10]]''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2017 || ''[[Trideviyaan]]'' || Cameo || [[SAB TV]]\n|-\n| ''[[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 11)|Bigg Boss 11]]'' || Guest || [[Colors TV]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2018 ||''Sajan Re Phir Se Jhoot Mat Bolo'' || Jaya || [[SAB TV]]\n|-\n| ''[[Box Cricket League|Box Cricket League 3]]'' || rowspan=3|Contestant || [[MTV India]]\n|-\n| ''Comedy Dangal'' || [[&TV]]\n|-\n| ''[[Comedy Circus]]''|| [[Sony Entertainment Television]]\n|-\n| 2018&ndash;2019 || ''[[Naagin (2015 TV series)|Naagin 3]]'' || Vishakha Khanna