on 2: The King is Back]]'' (2011)\n* ''[[Traffic Signal (film)|Traffic Signal]]'' (2009)\n* ''[[Ekk Deewana Tha]]'' (2012)\n* ''[[Talaash (2012 film)|Talaash]]'' (2012)\n* ''[[Vishwaroopam|Vishwaroop]]'' (2013)\n* ''[[Mohenjo Daro (film)|Mohenjo Daro]]'' (2016)\n* ''[[Raees (film)|Raees]]'' (2017)\n* ''[[Dil Dhadakne Do]]'' (2015)\n*''[[Rock On 2]]''\n*''[[Paltan (film)|Paltan]]'' (2018)\n*''[[Namastey England]]'' (2018)\n*''[[Gully Boy]]'' (2019)\n*''[[Panga (film)|Panga]]''(2020)\n{{col-end}}\n\n==See also==\n{{portal|Poetry}}\n* [[List of Urdu-language poets]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n* Chopra, Anupama, ''Sholay \u2013 The Making of a Classic'' (Penguin Books) 2000 {{ISBN|0-14-029970-X}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20120302011959/http://javedakhtar.bookchums.com/ Javed Akhtar Songs, Poetry, Biography]\n* [http://www.kavitakosh.org/kk/index.php?title=%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B5%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A6_%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%BC%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0 Javed Akhtar at Kavita Kosh] (Hindi)\n* {{IMDb name|id=0015287|name=Javed Akhtar}}\n* [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/hardtalk/5312158.stm BBC's Noel Thompson interviews JavedAkhtar on 4 September 2006]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20141215204433/http://javedakhtar.com/ JavedAkhtar.com]\n* [http://www.jakhira.com/search/label/javed-akhtar/ Javed Akhtar at Jakhira.com] (Hindi)\n* [http://shayaribazaar.com/ye-waqt-kya-hai-shayari-of-javed-akhtar// Javed Akhtar Shayaris]\n*[[Somesh Mathur]]\n\n{{Salim-Javed|state=expanded}}\n{{National Film Award Best Lyrics}}\n{{FilmfareAwardBestLyricist}}\n{{FilmfareAwardBestDialogue}}\n{{FilmfareLifetimeAchievementAward}}\n{{PadmaBhushanAwardRecipients 2000\u201309}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Akhtar, Javed}}\n[[Category:Indian male poets]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Padma Shri in arts]]\n[[Category:Urdu poets from India]]\n[[Category:Aligarh Muslim University alumni]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Padma B